 - Add a local 'i915' variable to reduce gt->i915 usage.  (Caz)
 - Drop unused 'intel_gt_read_register' prototype.  (Caz)

v3:
 - Drop unnecessary comment text.  (Lucas)
 - Drop unused register bit definition.  (Lucas)

